  "body": "### Preconditions\r\n- Composer shouldn't be resized manually\r\n- Composer must be empty from text\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Paste/type text into composer\r\n2. Pay attention to composer opacity level\r\n3. Pay attention at Send button UI\r\n4. Continue typing/pasting text into composer until it is fully expanded\r\n5. Collapse composer\r\n6. See if Jump to button is located above composer\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/97434915/0d8038f1-d70d-4e1f-95de-ffcdd207a2a1\r\n\r\n#### Actual results: \r\n2. Composer is transparent\r\n3. Send button opacity is not 100% and has white square background \r\n6. Jump Button partly hidden under the composer\r\n\r\n![photo_2023-05-26_15-14-41](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/97434915/2154e2c8-75cc-4f9a-ac3a-aac297152051)\r\n![photo_2023-05-26_15-18-20](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/97434915/5fc1a94c-3deb-4fe0-9636-725ca48d456f)\r\n![photo_2023-05-26_15-18-43](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/97434915/c395fe73-9547-4cae-9f21-31483c600c4d)\r\n\r\n#### Expected results:\r\n2. Composer is not transparent\r\n3. Send button has 100% opacity with no background\r\n6. Jump Button sticks to the top of the composer\r\n\r\n#### Additional Info:\r\nDevice: Redmi Note 8 Pro\r\nOS: MIUI Global 12.0.8 Stable\r\n",
